openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: 'test'
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /entity/{id}:
    parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        required: true
        schema:
          type: integer
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: 'test'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - key
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - getEntity
    put:
      responses:
        200:
          description: 'test'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - key
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - putEntity
